//www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-2024-mtv-vmas-3792869">MTV VMA 上主持和表演</a>。</p><p>在对《Megan》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/megan-thee-stallion-megan-album-review-3770938">四星评论</a>中，Karen Gwee 为<em>NME</em>写道：“Megan Thee Stallion 的方方面面在她的整个职业生涯中都得到了展现，从即兴风格到混音带再到录音室专辑。但到目前为止，他们的声音还没有如此有凝聚力（是的，甚至是“Worthy”，其合唱和活泼的流行吉他节拍是自我赋权的口号）。当《Cobra》中火热的吉他独奏响起时，它护送我们走出专辑——并预示着梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) 无所畏惧的新时代。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-announces-new-documentary-in-her-words-3802734">Megan Thee Stallion 宣布新纪录片《In Her Words》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
布鲁克林说唱歌手 Ka 去世，享年 52 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/brooklyn-rapper-ka-has-died-ages-52-3802731?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=brooklyn-rapper-ka-has-died-ages-52Surej Singh Tue, 15 Oct 2024 01:29:05 +0000 Music NewsNews..Hip-hopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3802731 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位说唱歌手也是一名长期的消防员，于八月发行了他的最新专辑</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brooklyn-rapper-ka-has-died-aged-52-3802731">布鲁克林后说唱歌手 Ka 去世，享年 52 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ka-2014@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>受人尊敬的布鲁克林独立说唱歌手 Ka 去世，享年 52 岁。</p><p>卡（Ka）的真名是卡西姆·瑞安（Kaseem Ryan），他的遗产管理机构通过社交媒体宣布，他于 10 月 12 日“意外”去世，享年 52 岁。声明中写道：“卡在布鲁克林布朗斯维尔出生和长大，过着为他的城市、他的社区、他的音乐服务的生活。作为一名在纽约市消防局工作 20 年的老兵，他冒着生命危险保护同胞。卡晋升为纽约消防局队长，并于 2001 年 9 月 11 日世贸中心袭击事件中担任急救人员。”</p><p>它继续说道：“作为一名唱片艺术家，他留下了非凡的遗产，包括十一张出色的自行发行的个人专辑。卡身后留下了妻子、母亲和妹妹。我们恳请尊重卡家人和亲人的隐私，因为他们对这一无法估量的损失感到悲痛。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBHcGIlv0WE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.