要的研究和倡议，以帮助全球抗击癌症<a href="https://t.co/wCniswYgW0">pic.twitter.com/wCniswYgW0</a></p><p> — The Cure (@thecure) <a href="https://twitter.com/thecure/status/1845890290596356248?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 10 月 14 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>这支标志性乐队正准备于 11 月 1 日发行《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">Songs Of A Lost World</a> 》，这是他们 16 年来的首张专辑。</p><p>史密斯最近透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-have-another-new-album-thats-virtually-finished-and-another-to-come-3802243">他们已经在制作另一张新专辑，“几乎完成”，第三张唱片也在酝酿之中</a>。他还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-2025-world-songs-lost-world-tour-2029-anniversary-tim-pope-documentary-3802253">分享了 2025 年世界巡演的计划，并谈到了乐队即将到来的 50 周年纪念日</a>。</p><p>此外，史密斯表示，他认为该乐队将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cure-treat-hyde-park-sprawling-career-spanning-set-european-show-2018-2351504">2018 年海德公园的头条表演</a>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robert-smith-says-hed-arranged-for-everything-to-end-for-the-cure-in-2018-3802082">分道扬镳</a>，并称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cures-robert-smith-says-dynamic-ticket-pricing-is-a-scam-and-driven-by-greed-3802210">动态门票定价是“由贪婪驱动”的“骗局”</a> 。</p><p>在采访的另一部分中，这位音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-album-art-meaning-janez-pirnat-death-3802369">解释了《失落世界之歌》封面艺术背后的深刻巧合和死亡</a>。史密斯还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-robert-smith-brother-death-never-can-say-goodbye-meaning-lyrics-songs-lost-world-interview-3802298">谈到了创作歌曲“I Can Never Say Goodbye”，讲述他哥哥的去世</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Cure 乐队的 Robert Smith 在 2022 年 BandLab NME 大奖上公布了完成的专辑名称" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/skpB48MCZhY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrer